<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456>
    bibo:endPage "49" ;
    bibo:journal "ZooKeys" ;
    bibo:startPage "11" ;
    bibo:volume "975" ;
    dc:creator "Hendrich, Lars; Watts, Chris H. S.; Balke, Michael" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "The \" minute diving beetles \" of southern Australia - taxonomic revision of Gibbidessus Watts, 1978, with description of six new species (Coleoptera, Dytiscidae, Bidessini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures8-11>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figure13>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures20-21>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figure30>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figure31>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures18-19>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures24-25> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures8-11>
    dc:description "Figures 8 - 11. Habitus of 8 G. pictipes, male 9 G. pictipes, female 10 G. rottnestensis sp. nov., male 11 G. rottnestensis sp. nov., female. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/462662" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Head of G. pictipes A without cervical line (red arrows), and of G. rottnestensis sp. nov. B without cervical line but rather a few punctures instead (red arrows)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/462664" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures20-21>
    dc:description "Figures 20, 21. 20 Gibbidessus pictipes 21 G. rottnestensis sp. nov. A median lobe in ventral view B median lobe in lateral view, left side C left paramere in lateral view, D right paramere in lateral view. Scale bar: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/462668" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figure30>
    dc:description "Figure 30. Habitat of Gibbidessus pictipes. A, B Seasonally flooded and exposed wetland with Baumea and sedges 3 km ENE Manypeaks, Lake Pleasant Nature Reserve." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/462675" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figure31>
    dc:description "Figure 31. Habitat of Gibbidessus pictipes. A, B Seasonally flooded sedge swamp around lake Nalyerin C deeper and more permanent part of the lake, with stands of Baumea." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/462676" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures18-19>
    dc:description "Figures 18, 19. 18 Gibbidessus kangarooensis sp. nov. 19 G. pederzanii sp. nov. A median lobe in ventral view B median lobe in lateral view, left side C left paramere in lateral view D right paramere in lateral view. Scale bar: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/462667" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.975.55456.figures24-25>
    dc:description "Figures 24, 25. Distribution of 24 Gibbidessus pictipes (black dots) 25 G. pederzanii sp. nov. (red dot), G. rottnestensis sp. nov. (blue dots)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/462670" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

